# Copy this file to .env for local config.

# Acton loads .env automatically.



# === TonAPI / TON Console (https://tonconsole.com — project API key) ===
# 1) tonconsole.com → project "Phalanx PLX" → TonAPI → Create API key
# 2) Paste below; verify: .scripts/ops/test-tonapi-key.ps1
# 3) Same TONAPI_KEY on Railway (plx-toolkit) + Cloudflare Pages if web calls TonAPI
# Guide: docs/TON-CONSOLE-PLX.md

# TONAPI_KEY=          # dari TonAPI → API keys di tonconsole.com
# CONSOLE_TOKEN=       # alias yang sama (load-env menyalin ke TONAPI_KEY jika kosong)

# === PLX mainnet addresses (for toolkit / scripts — optional in .env) ===
